---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<BaseLayout title="The Narthex" description="Entry points for the curious — universal human questions that open doors to an ancient tradition.">

  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:40px;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:16px;">The Narthex</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:34px;">Begin with What's Real</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        These questions aren't about religion. They're about reality. Start with whichever one pulls you in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container" style="padding-bottom:80px;">
    <div class="narthex-hub-grid">

      <a href={`${base}/narthex/beauty/`} class="narthex-hub-card">
        <div class="narthex-hub-img-wrap">
          <img src={`${base}/images/hagia-sophia-interior.jpg`} alt="Interior of Hagia Sophia" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="narthex-hub-body">
          <h3>"Why does beauty matter?"</h3>
          <p>Why do we build cathedrals instead of warehouses? What ancient Christians understood about beauty that we've forgotten.</p>
          <span class="narthex-hub-meta">9 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href={`${base}/narthex/ancient-faith/`} class="narthex-hub-card">
        <div class="narthex-hub-img-wrap">
          <img src={`${base}/images/ravenna-sant-apollinare.jpg`} alt="Mosaic procession from Ravenna" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="narthex-hub-body">
          <h3>"What did ancient Christians actually believe?"</h3>
          <p>Before the splits, before the denominations — what did the first thousand years of Christianity look like?</p>
          <span class="narthex-hub-meta">10 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href={`${base}/narthex/beyond-materialism/`} class="narthex-hub-card">
        <div class="narthex-hub-img-wrap">
          <img src={`${base}/images/sinai-monastery.jpg`} alt="St. Catherine's Monastery, Sinai" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="narthex-hub-body">
          <h3>"Is there more to reality than what we can measure?"</h3>
          <p>A tradition that never had a war with science, because it never reduced truth to only what is empirical.</p>
          <span class="narthex-hub-meta">10 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href={`${base}/narthex/prayer/`} class="narthex-hub-card">
        <div class="narthex-hub-img-wrap">
          <img src={`${base}/images/cefalu-pantocrator.jpg`} alt="Christ Pantocrator, Cefalù" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="narthex-hub-body">
          <h3>"What if prayer isn't what you think it is?"</h3>
          <p>Not talking at God. Not asking for things. Something older, quieter, and far more transformative.</p>
          <span class="narthex-hub-meta">9 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .narthex-hub-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .narthex-hub-card {
    background: var(--gold-06);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--gold-10);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .narthex-hub-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-40);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .narthex-hub-img-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .narthex-hub-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.4s;
  }
  .narthex-hub-card:hover .narthex-hub-img-wrap img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .narthex-hub-body {
    padding: 24px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .narthex-hub-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--beeswax);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .narthex-hub-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--censer-smoke);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .narthex-hub-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--deep-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .narthex-hub-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
